[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1404932","time":"2018-12-16 23:44","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"(媛娇系是检验大法的唯一标准)","message":"我记得网页本来就可以开socket吧？","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/14/131492.jpg","floor":"#2-1","id":"1404970","time":"2018-12-17 02:49","userId":"misakaxindex","userName":"東瀬まつり太","userSign":"","message":"网页的websocket没法直连c的socket的啦"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/41/90/419012.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1404938","time":"2018-12-16 23:57","userId":"ekibun","userName":"ekibun","userSign":"","message":"webpack？","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/14/131492.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1404969","time":"2018-12-17 02:40","userId":"misakaxindex","userName":"東瀬まつり太","userSign":"","message":"已经试过browserify啦，明天试试webpack<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/80/178081.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1404941","time":"2018-12-17 00:03","userId":"ershiwo","userName":"板砖加身","userSign":"(大破的那珂酱好萌！)","message":"websocket？","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/14/131492.jpg","floor":"#4-1","id":"1404968","time":"2018-12-17 02:39","userId":"misakaxindex","userName":"東瀬まつり太","userSign":"","message":"websocket不能连上c程序里的unix socket"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/79/267979.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1404949","time":"2018-12-17 00:29","userId":"banixc","userName":"233","userSign":"","message":"web只能使用websocket，跟socket是两个东西，虽然本质上websocket也是socket，但两个概念的层级不一样，websocket是应用层协议。<br>nodejs的包是不能在浏览器上运行的，因为node是个后端语言，而浏览器只能基于HTTP类协议。有一种方案是 web -> websocket -> nodes websocket server -> socket -> c socket server。<br>Android的话可以直接发起socket连接到C的socket server。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/14/131492.jpg","floor":"#5-1","id":"1404965","time":"2018-12-17 02:35","userId":"misakaxindex","userName":"東瀬まつり太","userSign":"","message":"这层层转发也太麻烦了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">不过不失为是一种websocket连接 socket的方法<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/68/286878.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1404956","time":"2018-12-17 00:50","userId":"yejingchen","userName":"菜叶","userSign":"(你的爱还不够啊！)","message":"感觉配一配 webpack 把你要的包打进去就可以用 es6 import？（瞎猜","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/14/131492.jpg","floor":"#6-1","id":"1404966","time":"2018-12-17 02:37","userId":"misakaxindex","userName":"東瀬まつり太","userSign":"","message":"刚才试了下browserify，不知道是不是设置错了没有效果，明天试试webpack"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/61/76150.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1404964","time":"2018-12-17 01:45","userId":"binota","userName":"\"","userSign":"","message":"net 是 node.js 的東西，得換成其他用 JS 實現的包才行<br><br><span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">不過也得是 HTTP 才行</span>","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/14/131492.jpg","floor":"#7-1","id":"1404967","time":"2018-12-17 02:38","userId":"misakaxindex","userName":"東瀬まつり太","userSign":"","message":"js的包几乎都是websocket实现的？websocket没法连c的socket啊_(:з」∠)_"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/61/76150.jpg","floor":"#7-2","id":"1404972","time":"2018-12-17 04:16","userId":"binota","userName":"\"","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">東瀬まつり太</span> 说: js的包几乎都是websocket实现的？websocket没法连c的socket啊_(:з」∠)_</q></div>因為目前只支持 HTTP 跟 WebSocket 兩種 Protocol"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/59/55968.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1404991","time":"2018-12-17 09:29","userId":"zodiacg","userName":"zodiacg","userSign":"(那谁谁家那小谁)","message":"5l说法是对的，层级不一样，websocket跟socket完全是两个东西。浏览器内的连接只能构建在http之上而不是之下。你非要浏览器里连到普通的socket必须要有一个websocket2socket的server来转发。或者你干脆用c实现一个websocket的服务端，那客户端就就简单多了<br><br>npm的滥用导致server-side js(node)跟browser js容易混淆，不是什么js都能webpack之类的打包然后扔浏览器里运行的。electron不是一个没菜单栏的浏览器那么简单，之所以要有它就是因为这种区别。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/14/131492.jpg","floor":"#8-1","id":"1405023","time":"2018-12-17 12:20","userId":"misakaxindex","userName":"東瀬まつり太","userSign":"","message":"懂了，websocket其实也是基于http的，浏览器里实现不了原生socket"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/02/204.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1405001","time":"2018-12-17 10:37","userId":"mono","userName":"rnono","userSign":"(汝视视汝)","message":"浏览器开放给JS的网络功能只限 (不完整的) 应用层。如果开放更下层，上层的安全策略如CORS就没意义了。<br><br>有流言说electron将来可能不打包巨大的chromium那一半，在有chrome的机器就能跑","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/76/287622.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1405050","time":"2018-12-17 13:26","userId":"trim21","userName":"Trim21","userSign":"(异端比异教徒更可恨)","message":"你可以先解决跑在web里的问题, 然后用混合应用移植到安卓上去<br><br>省劲的意义上, 直接写一个node服务端转发吧...","sub":[]}]